# 💈 Barbershop Website

A clean, responsive, and modern **barbershop landing page** built with **HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap**.  
This website showcases the barber’s services, prices, and contact details, and includes a responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📱 **Fully Responsive** — Works perfectly on all devices.
- 🎨 **Modern Design** — Clean, warm color palette and smooth hover effects.
- 📷 **Image Carousel** — Showcasing barbershop photos.
- ✂️ **Services Section** — With prices and descriptions.
- 📍 **Contact Section** — Phone, Telegram, and location links.
- 🖱 **Smooth Navigation** — With mobile-friendly hamburger menu.

---

## 🛠 Built With

- **HTML5** — Semantic and accessible markup.
- **CSS3** — Custom styles with responsive media queries.
- **Bootstrap 5** — Carousel, grid layout, and responsive helpers.

---

## 📂 Folder Structure

```bash
barbershop/
│
├── index.html       # Main HTML file
├── style.css        # Custom CSS styles
├── bootstrap.css    # Bootstrap framework
├── images/          # All project images
└── README.md        # Project documentation

